==English==

===Pronunciation===
*IPA: /ˈbʊʧ.ɝ/

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A [[person]] who [[prepare]]s and [[sell]]s [[meat]] (and sometimes also [[slaughter]]s the [[animal]]s).
# A [[brutal]] or [[indiscriminate]] [[killer]].
# ([[Cockney rhyming slang]], via ''butcher's hook'') A [[look]].
# A person who sells candy, drinks, etc. in theatres, trains, [[circus]]es , etc. (old, informal).

